These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, entrepreneur, coach
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cucumber, peach
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, writing
City: berlin, edinburgh, nizza
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, malaysian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, chaman, blend
 1. the person traveling to berlin is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
 2. the australian is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 3. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 4. the malaysian is somewhere between the freelancer and the blend-smoker##7
 5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the entrepreneur is the havana-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is not the british##6
 8. the australian is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the blend-smoker is not the person who's hobby is writing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Job      | freelancer       | entrepreneur  | coach     |
| Food          | peach       | cucumber  | carrot    |
| Hobby         | card-games  | writing   | traveling |
| City   | berlin | nizza   | edinburgh     |
| Nationality   | australian  | malaysian | british   |
| Cigar           | chaman  | havana      | blend  |

