7. the indonesian is the social-worker##1
8. the person who likes ivory is somewhere between the person eating chinchillarot and the person who growsaconite##7
9. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the person eating chinchillarot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | daffodil       | orchid      | aconite    |
| Food          | chinchillarot     | papaya        | kiwi        |
| Job           | architect  | social-worker | fisherman   |
| Color   | chestnut | ivory           | mauve |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | indonesian    | malaysian   |
| Pet     | cat        | rabbit          | chinchilla         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-18::.
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, new-york
There 3 different types of food: corn, pepper, pomegranate
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, manager, musician
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat, blend
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, yellow, lilac
3 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, mouse
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 3. the person eating corn is the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the blend-smoker and the game-smoker##7
 5. the journalist is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 6. the manager is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
 7. the journalist is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person who likes lilac##2
 8. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
 9. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
10. the person eating corn is not the manager##6
11. the blend-smoker is on the right of the journalist##1
12. the journalist is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| City      | edinburgh      | san-francisco | new-york      |
| Food          | pepper    | corn          | pomegranate |
| Job           | manager   | journalist    | musician    |
| Cigar   | game | baccarat       | blend      |
| Color   | blood-red   | yellow           | lilac      |
| Pet           | mouse     | cat           | guinea-pig  |

