| Game         | whist  | scrabble | mah-jongg  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | drama       | western |
| Nationality   | turkish      | thai        | colombian  |
| Job         | bartender    | lawyer  | videographer    |
| Transport     | roller      | motorbike   | bike    |

