.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, nurse, paramedic
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, whist
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, dutch
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, house, pop
There 3 different types of food: grapes, cranberry, apple
 1. the accountant is not the fan of salsa##6
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the owner of the turtle##7
 4. the paramedic is the person playing whist##1
 5. the fan of salsa is the person playing whist##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
 7. the fan of house is on the right of the accountant##1
 8. the american is the person eating apple##1
 9. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
10. the owner of the goldfish is the person playing monopoly##1
11. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Job           | paramedic    | accountant | nurse    |
| Game   | whist       | monopoly    | mah-jongg   |
| Nationality   | dutch        | colombian  | american |
| Pet           | turtle       | goldfish   | pony     |
| Music-Genre         | salsa | pop | house |
| Food     | cranberry       | grapes | apple    |

 